dc:title: Processed Covid Cases in EU from 2020 to 2023
dc:creator: Fabian Hupfeld
dc:subject: Covid 19 cases per week
dc:description: This Dataset contains weekly covid 19 cases in europa per country from 2020-2023
Column country_code: observed country as a 2 letter isocode
Column rate_14_day: 14-day notification rate of newly reported COVID-19 cases per 100 000 population
